Package org.framed.orm.ui.editPart.connectionkinds

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ORMFulfillmentEditPart
    This EditPart is the controller for Relations from type fulfillment.
    ORMRelationEditPart
    This EditPart is the super/parent EditPart also super/parent controller of all Relations.
    ORMRelationshipConstraintEditPart
    This EditPart is the super/parent EditPart respectively super/parent controller of all Relations from type cyclic, total, acyclic, reflexive and irreflexive (aka relationshipConstraint) and is required as all relationshipConstraints of a Relation from type relationship need to be unified in a single figure.
    ORMRelationshipEditPart
    This EditPart is the controller for Relations from type relationship.
